{"tid":1427340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍絲風向撚] 長輩圖文宣催淚彈禍害","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:30.000Z","uid":100004,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ab517dcc0f45028ee64ec9e7fd5abe8f0b9bd130","tid":1427340,"uid":100004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:49:56.000Z","msg":"對於坐起屋企unun腳，深夜街都唔出街既藍絲<br />\n成場反送中最貼身係d咩？一定係起屋企附近放既催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不可不管！远距离吸入催泪弹等于慢性自杀，不可不知的催泪弹4大危害</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />催淚彈原來係神經毒氣<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">可能</span></span>會致命致盲傷腦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />催淚彈<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">可能</span></span>會因為煙囪效應上到廿樓，老人小童吸入會影響腦部功能<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長時間接觸催淚彈<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">可能</span></span>比水銀毒性更強<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />催淚彈<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">可能</span></span>殘留起街市超市，慢性毒素會經被感染食物慢慢積累人體<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩湯水推薦可以補身同<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">可能</span></span>預防催淚彈禍害<br />\n<br />\n用長輩圖/片包裝成婦女新知<br />\n等d師奶自己起藍絲group不斷share出去<br />\n下次班狗再放催淚彈話唔定屌番佢地轉頭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出面幾亂都好，保護家人健康最重要<br />\n認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"732d5699dcd8f52d29767abdf4c029ab75457ed7","tid":1427340,"uid":100004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8afc5889102a0e9e36772a6bf4a655546c1faa53","tid":1427340,"uid":262875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fc4ee913507403a138f6178665f48445373c